data.description: Welcome to 13003 Mills Edge Ct! This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath has 2 more bonus rooms in the lower level. The home has 12' ceilings in the great room and master bathroom and double trey ceiling in the master bedroom. Cozy up to the fireplace in the great room on those cold winter nights. The great room and kitchen has waterproof luxury vinyl flooring. The kitchen has white cabinetry and a large walk-in pantry. The double doors lead out to the deck where you can enjoy family time while putting your favorite foods on the grill.  In the lower level you will find a very large family room - great for entertaining or just relaxing watching T.V. In addition to 2 more bedrooms making this a 5 bedroom home. HOA $100/year. Schedule your showing Today
